Spotify-To-Streamer.Bot V 0.1 ( by LeBluxTV )
This allow viewers to add song to your spotify song queue

*OBS WS v5.x*{.obs-version-badge} 
# Tutorial Video

In order to get full functionality, such like, [ !sr artistName , songName ] to add song to queue , you MUST be premium spotify user.
it's not only because not being premium will cast ads too, but it's a spotify API limitation.

# Configuration 
Go to https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard/ to create your application and receive your client Id & client Secret codes
add the redirect URI in edit settings : http://127.0.0.1:1300/spotifyOAuthRedirectUri/ 
Commands for the first connection is !spotifyConnect .
Other commands are : !sPlay !sPause !sNext !sPrev !sQueue and !sr artistName , songName to add a song to the queue.
